thread.title: Janet Hardy
thread.title_full: Peaches Boutique reviewed by Janet Hardy

author: Janet Hardy
title: Janet Hardy
text: This is my first time using Peaches. I had to send the first dress back due to a fitting issue. They were beyond helpful and very pleasant. Ordered a replacement dress. I've always used Promgirl but I will definitely keep ordering from Peaches as long as the service continues to be excellent.
